1-->The perfit commit:
* add the right changes
* compose a good commit message
more topics mixed in the commit is harder to understand.
GIT STAGING AREA concept is allows you to select specific files.
in terminal,
$git status get status.
$ git add css/general.css --add css file
& git diff index.html--another file index html ,we can see what changes it currently contains
two parts of changes,first one belong to next commit topic,but not second one
we can add first part to the staging area,
4 git add-p index.html--we can decide what to add what to not
